'''Shabda Ratnakaram''' is a [[Telugu language]] dictionary written by B. Sitaramacharyulu.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dli.ernet.in/cgi-bin/DBscripts/allmetainfo.cgi?barcode=2990120001412|title=Shabda Ratnakaram|author=B. Sitaramacharyulu|date=|work=|publisher=|accessdate=11 February 2012}}{{dead link|date=May 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.weekendcreations.com/tollywood_talk.php?talk_id=1641#.Tzs1pOVzUVA|title= Damarukam|author= |date= |work= |publisher= |accessdate=11 February 2012}}</ref> It is known as one of the Telugu literary accomplishment.

